    "ap_p": "<p>NEST Group is a multi-sector group company that has been operating since 2018 across investment, investment advisory, financial management, real estate, non-banking financial services, tourism, food service, and labor placement.</p><p>With a professional team, we ensure synergy across our subsidiaries — delivering comprehensive solutions and real value to clients and investors, and building an environment where we grow sustainably together.</p><p>Our activities go beyond service delivery: we open new opportunities and spread new experiences and culture. We uphold international standards and place quality, trust, and a customer-centric approach at the heart of everything we do.</p><p>Under the slogan \"Towards a more amazing tomorrow,\" we aim to make a tangible contribution to social and economic development and create positive impact.</p>",
